data.description: The Juniper combines all the amenities of single family living with all the conveniences of a townhome into one design youâll love calling home. The welcoming foyer features a huge closet conveniently placed. The main level is open and airy, with a large, well-designed kitchen thatâs open to the living area so youâll never miss a conversation, this level also includes a powder room.  A dining area provides a great space for entertaining or cozy evenings at home. The upstairs has a total of 3 large bedrooms, each with plenty of closet space, a laundry closet that can hold a full-size washer and dryer.  The ownerâs suite is a quiet retreat and features its own full bath and a huge walk-in closet (another full bath is in the hallway by the other 2 bedrooms). The lower level provides plenty of storage space, or space for a workroom. To Be Built. Photos for representation only.
